This paper deals with the problem of license plate recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques for license plate recognition, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves image processing techniques, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the security implications of license plate recognition, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR).
